== Audiobook ==
In August 2023, &quot;Thieves&#x27; World&quot; was released as an audiobook on Audible, published by Tantor Media and narrated by Jonathan Johns.

==Board game==
* &quot;Sanctuary: Thieves&#x27; World&quot; (Mayfair Games, 1982).

